{"tid":371010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火災被救豬隻 事後被製成香腸送消防隊","createTime":"2017-08-23T11:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T06:43:37.000Z","uid":54627,"like":710,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f145812462e139a9a9b78c8a8e3d9b8f7acb0772","tid":371010,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/191703_01e2dcab42d74c44045270c19e57264f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F191703_01e2dcab42d74c44045270c19e57264f.jpg&h=8bdd15dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國西部的威爾特郡一處農場發生火災，被消防隊救出的2頭母豬及18隻小豬<br />\n半年後被灌製成香腸贈送給當初救豬的消防隊。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月威爾特郡的一處農場豬圈發生火災，當時消防隊員搶救出母豬2頭及18隻小豬仔，在過了半年後的這個月飼主將這批獲救的豬隻送往屠宰場處理並將其灌製成香腸，當成禮物分送給當地消防署。<br />\n<br />\n飼主表示， 素食(動保)主義者應該會厭惡這種行為，但獲得贈送的消防隊則對吃到BBQ香腸相當開心，直說超棒的值得推薦的美味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/japanese/41020587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fjapanese%2F41020587&d=JMzn%2FmBfnRP%2F7ql3QMWPqRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7de8f82a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fjapanese%2F41020587&h=8c435622\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/japanese/41020587</a>"},{"pid":"82105ff6862b9f98df057b4ed31f4345f0ef9299","tid":371010,"uid":20058,"like":394,"dislike":5,"score":389,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:18:43.000Z","msg":"救左同冇救有咩分別<br />\n反正都要死"},{"pid":"ea4b43ec2da17e05ebd195cae704478650d8248d","tid":371010,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebc87358b27325a108c94306204efce29d3d9f5","tid":371010,"uid":22932,"like":264,"dislike":3,"score":261,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救左同冇救有咩分別<br />\n反正都要死</blockquote><br